eezingtons]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[Record producer|production]] \n* [[Needlz]]&nbsp;\u2013 production, songwriting\n{{col-2}}\n* [[Saint Cassius (musician)|Khalil Walton]]&nbsp;\u2013 songwriting\n* [[Manny Marroquin]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[Audio mixing (recorded music)|mixing]]\n* Christian Plata&nbsp;\u2013 mixing assistant\n* Erik Madrid&nbsp;\u2013 mixing assistant\n* [[Stephen Marcussen]]&nbsp;- [[Audio mastering|mastering]]\n{{col-end}}\nCredits adapted from the liner notes of ''Doo-Wops & Hooligans'', Elektra Records<ref name=\"Notes\"/>\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n=== Weekly charts ===\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"|Chart (2010\u201311)\n!scope=\"col\"|Peak<br/>position\n|-\n{{singlechart|Australia|1|artist=Bruno Mars|song=Just the Way You Are|accessdate=November 20, 2010|refname=\"ARIAS\"|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Austria|1|artist=Bruno Mars|song=Just the Way You Are|accessdate=November 28, 2010|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Flanders|4|artist=Bruno Mars|song=Just the Way You Are|accessdate=November 28, 2010|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Wallonia|17|artist=Bruno Mars|song=Just the Way You Are|accessdate=November 28, 2010|refname=FLA|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Canada|1|artist=Bruno Mars|accessdate=October 17, 2010|refname=\"CAN\"|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Billboardcanadaac|1|artist=Bruno Mars|accessdate=October 4, 2019|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Billboardcanadachrtop40|1|artist=Bruno Mars|accessdate=June 17, 2019|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Billboardcanadahotac|1|artist=Bruno Mars|accessdate=October 4, 2019|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Czech Republic|14|artist=Bruno Mars|song=Just the Way You Are|accessdate=November 28, 2010|year=2011|week=02|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Denmark|6|artist=Bruno Mars|song=Just the Way You Are|accessdate=November 28, 2010|refname=DEN|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Finland|17|artist=Bruno